# The PyPI package is the algorithm only. The interactive visualiser (web/) and
# the figure studio (simulations/) are learning/dev tooling — they live in the
# repo but must never ship in the sdist or wheel. The wheel already contains only
# ds_msp* (see [tool.setuptools.packages.find]); this keeps the sdist lean too.
prune web
prune simulations
global-exclude *.tsbuildinfo *.map .DS_Store
